Title: Balance Without Violence
Description: Some of the fish that the Unga hozen have gathered don't seem do be dead yet. There may still be time to throw them back into the water.
ObjectivesText: Throw 6 Flailing Carp into Nayeli Lagoon.
RewardText:
The grateful fish swim happily toward the safety of the middle of the lagoon.

With any luck, they will be eaten by crocolisks.

Objectives.Text: Throw Flailing Carp back into the water
